                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080713-25-defend296 t18080713-25-punish161"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
